results.name: Even permutational numbers A134640.
mathematica: a = {}; b = {}; Do[AppendTo[b, n]; w =Permutations[b]; Do[j = FromDigits[w[[m]], n + 1]; If[OddQ[j], AppendTo[a, j]], {m, 1, Length[w]}], {n, 0, 10}]; a (*Artur Jasinski*)
